		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I do not have a diagram no. I looked up pinouts for the EXP connector and the 15 pin on this site and others and matched pin to pin. <br /><br />Quite a few other accessories should work.. just off the top of my head..<br /><br />Family trainer accessories (japanese powerpad et al)<br />Famicom 4 player adapters (different than US ones, required for 4 player FC games)<br />Famicom 3D glasses (tested, working at this point and time)<br />Famicom Basic (keyboard)<br />Famicom Modem (special controller)<br /><br />etc

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


